OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FAston Villa fans say they've been left
OL,7,F"disappointed" and "gutted" at missing
OL,8,Fthe club's Europa League open-top bus
OL,9,Fparade.
OL,11,FVilla thrashed German side Freiburg 3-
OL,12,F0 at the Besiktas Stadium in Istanbul
OL,13,Flast night to win their first European
OL,14,Ftrophy in 44-years.
OL,16,FGoals from Youri Tielemans, Emi
OL,17,FBuendia, and Morgan Rogers secured the
OL,18,Fvictory in an unforgettable night for
OL,19,Fthousands of fans across the world.
OL,26,@tD@L{ytD@Q{y
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
