OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779397867
OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FBut, as the ticker tape settled, Aston
OL,7,FVilla and Birmingham City Council
OL,8,Fannounced plans for the club's parade.
OL,10,FThey said the players and staff would
OL,11,Fbe back in Birmingham the next day,
OL,12,FThursday (May 21st), for the event.
OL,14,FIt would start at 4:30pm and begin on
OL,15,FBranston Street in the Jewellery
OL,16,FQuarter and cover a route of
OL,17,Fapproximately 4.5km, taking in Sand
OL,18,FPits, Broad Street, and Centenary
OL,19,FSquare.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
