OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FWhich, for many, came as a surprise,
OL,7,Fwith thousands of fans still in
OL,8,FTurkiye or working back home.
OL,10,FPeople responded to Aston Villa's post
OL,11,Fon X to voice their frustrations.
OL,13,FSeoulsister36 wrote: "So disappointed
OL,14,Fit's so quick. Thousands travelling
OL,15,Fback from Istanbul, people with not
OL,16,Fenough time to book time off work,
OL,17,Fchildren barely out of the school day.
OL,18,FNot every Villa fan lives in central
OL,19,FBrum! Gutted I can't get there."
OL,26,@pD@Bxz
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
