OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,Fdan villafan posted: "Ah man. Going to
OL,7,FIstanbul was completely undoable for
OL,8,Fus with a little one, but we hoped to
OL,9,Fbe in Birmingham for the parade but
OL,10,Fnot enough notice for us to get there
OL,11,Feven on a half day at work. Hope
OL,12,Feveryone that can make it, enjoys it.
OL,13,FUTV".
OL,15,FDan Clissett said: "Why can't it be
OL,16,Fdone a week on Saturday, play the City
OL,17,Fgame on Sunday, then let the player
OL,18,Fproperly celebrate all week surely
OL,19,Freporting to national team can wait a
OL,20,Fcouple of days and that way people who
OL,21,Fare in Istanbul can also celebrate."
OL,26,@nD@Dpo
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
