OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FMany more fans were concerned about
OL,7,Fnot making it to the parade.
OL,9,FBut the club have said they explored
OL,10,Fthe possibility of recreating the
OL,11,Ficonic 1982 European Cup celebrations
OL,12,Fby taking the players to Victoria
OL,13,FSquare, as well as erecting a stage in
OL,14,FCentenary Square.
OL,16,FBut due to ongoing works and safety
OL,17,Fconcerns at Victoria Square, and
OL,18,Fadvice from authorities around the
OL,19,Frisk of overcrowding at Centenary
OL,20,FSquare, both proposals were ruled out.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
