OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1779397867
OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FThe club added: "After returning from
OL,7,FIstanbul tomorrow, the squad is due to
OL,8,Fundertake a full training session on
OL,9,FFriday, before travelling to
OL,10,FManchester on Saturday ahead of
OL,11,FSunday's final Premier League fixture
OL,12,Fof the season against Manchester City."
OL,14,FBirmingham Pride also takes place in
OL,15,Fthe city centre on Saturday 23rd and
OL,16,FSunday 24th May.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
