OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FLawrence Barton, who is the director
OL,7,Fof Birmingham Pride, said: "Huge
OL,8,Fcongratulations to everyone at Aston
OL,9,FVilla FC for your fantastic success
OL,10,Flast night in Europe!
OL,12,F"We must clarify, however, that
OL,13,FBirmingham Pride is held on Saturday
OL,14,F23rd and Sunday 24th May of the Bank
OL,15,FHoliday and NOT Monday 25th.
OL,17,F"Any decision to not parade the cup on
OL,18,FMonday is not as a result of the
OL,19,FBirmingham Pride weekend."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
