OL,3,CFans 'disappointed' and 'gutted' over
OL,4,Cmissing Aston Villa's trophy parade
OL,6,FThe Villa players are due to report to
OL,7,Ftheir international squads ahead of
OL,8,Fthe FIFA World Cup on Monday, 25th May.
OL,10,FThey said these factors made Thursday,
OL,11,FMay 21st, the only viable option.
OL,13,FBut for those that can't make it, the
OL,14,Fclub have said they will be
OL,15,Flivestreaming the event on their
OL,16,Fsocial media.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
